        <https://doi.org/10.1038/s41586-020-03127-1>,
        <https://doi.org/10.1038/s42003-023-05290-3>,
        <https://doi.org/10.1094/PBIOMES-07-20-0051-R>,
        <https://doi.org/10.1111/gcbb.13094>,
